profile.profileDescription: Use this profile if you want a system that is compliant with Qualified Dublin Core

label.name: Description
label.description: An account of the resource.

label.name: Source of description
label.description: Source of item description. This should be a formal citation if possible. For informal sources a narrative description is acceptable.

label.name: Caption
label.description: Short descriptive caption for item.

label.name: Georeference
label.description: Coordinates documenting the location of the item

label.name: GeoNames
label.description: A Geographic lookup that takes search text, passes it to the GeoNames search service and provides a dropdown with search results (ordered by score). Selected geoname is stored as both text (name, country, continent and ID) and the service URL identifier.

label.name: Notes (internal use only)
label.description: Notes regarding item

label.name: Abstract
label.description: A summary of the resource.

label.name: Accrual Method
label.description: The method by which items are added to a collection.

label.name: Accrual Periodicity
label.description: The frequency with which items are added to a collection.

label.name: Accrual Policy
label.description: The policy governing the addition of items to a collection.

label.name: Audience
label.description: A class of entity for whom the resource is intended or useful.

label.name: Bibliographic Citation
label.description: Recommended practice is to include sufficient bibliographic detail to identify the resource as unambiguously as possible.

label.name: Conforms To
label.description: An established standard to which the described resource conforms.

label.name: Coverage
label.description: The spatial or temporal topic of the resource

label.name: Date
label.description: A point or period of time associated with an event in the lifecycle of the resource.

label.name: Education Level
label.description: A class of entity

label.name: Extent
label.description: The size or duration of the resource..

label.name: Format
label.description: The file format or physical medium or dimensions of the resource.

label.name: Instruction Method
label.description: A process

label.name: Language
label.description: A language of the resource.

label.name: License
label.description: A legal document giving official permission to do something with the resource.

label.name: Medium
label.description: The material or physical carrier of the resource.

label.name: Provenence
label.description: A statement of any changes in ownership and custody of the resource since its creation that are significant for its authenticity

label.name: Rights
label.description: Information about rights held in and over the resource.

label.name: Spacial Coverage
label.description: Spatial characteristics of the resource.

label.name: Subject
label.description: The topic of the resource.

label.name: Library of Congress Subject Headings
label.description: Library of Congress Subject headings describing this object. To add a new heading simply type the first few letters of the heading and choose the desired one from the displayed list of possible matches.

label.name: Table Of Contents
label.description: A list of subunits of the resource.

label.name: Temporal Coverage
label.description: Temporal characteristics of the resource..

label.name: Type
label.description: The nature or genre of the resource.

label.name: Alternate identifiers
label.description: Any additional unambiguous reference to the resource within a given context.

label.name: Valid
label.description: Date (often a range) of validity of a resource.

label.name: Box Title
label.description: Title given to box.

label.name: Box Number
label.description: Postcard box number printed on box ends.

label.name: Group
label.description: Subgroup of cards printed on clear mylar sheets that divide cards in box.

label.name: Item Number
label.description: Number in upper left corner on each postcard sleeve denoting chronological organization of each box (each box starts with #1).

label.name: Category
label.description: General classification of card.

label.name: Format
label.description: Information regarding format or medium.

label.name: Format Info
label.description: Indicates format or medium used when printing the card.

label.name: Orientation
label.description: View is displayed on card in horizontal or vertical manner.

label.name: View Direction
label.description: Indicates which direction the view lays (for instance

label.name: Time
label.description: Indicates whether view shows daytime or nighttime.

label.name: Interior
label.description: Check box if view is indoors.

label.name: Message
label.description: Check box if there's a message or note written on card other than an address.

label.name: Content Memo
label.description: Brief excerpt from particularly interesting messages.

label.name: Series
label.description: Numbers or letters issued to view by publisher.

label.name: Purchase
label.description: Price OYL paid for card usually found on back of card in pencil. Accuracy needs to be determined.

label.name: Card Text
label.description: Nature of text printed by publisher

label.name: Mailed?
label.description: Check if card was mailed.

label.name: Postmark Date
label.description: Year of postmark

label.name: City To
label.description: City to which card was mailed. Most of the addresses will be difficult to read.

label.name: State To
label.description: State to which card was mailed. If card was mailed abroad

label.name: City From
label.description: City from which card was mailed

label.name: State From
label.description: State from which card was mailed

label.name: PMC
label.description: Check if Private Mailing Card is printed on back of card.

label.name: View still exists?
label.description: Check if view exists anymore.

label.name: Additional Information
label.description: Pertinent information about card not mentioned elsewhere.

label.name: Completed Record?
label.description: Check after all information has been entered.

label.name: Copyright
label.description: Include date

label.name: Description
label.description: Narrative biography for entity. This is the primary text used to document the entity.

label.name: Source of description
label.description: Source of entity biography. This should be a formal citation if possible. For informal sources a narrative description is acceptable.
